    <p><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l7' data-llen='156:182'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '003-1a' );" name="003-1a" class="pb">[003-1a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l8' data-llen='182:190'>欽定四庫全書</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l9' data-llen='190:200'>　三家詩拾遺卷三</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l10' data-llen='200:221'>　　　　　　　　　　栁州府知府范家相撰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l11' data-llen='221:226'>　國風</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l12' data-llen='226:230'>關雎</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l13' data-llen='230:253'>　魯詩司馬遷曰周道缺詩人本之袵席關雎作又曰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l14' data-llen='253:276'>　周室衰而關雎作　劉向曰周之康王夫人晏而出</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l15' data-llen='276:299'>　朝關雎起興思得淑女以配君子夫雎鳩之鳥未嘗</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l16' data-llen='299:325'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '003-1b' );" name="003-1b" class="pb">[003-1b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l17' data-llen='325:352'>　見其乗居而匹處也<span class='krp-note'>列女/傳</span>杜欽曰珮玉晏鳴關雎刺</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l18' data-llen='352:375'>　之知好色之伐性短年離制度之生無厭天下将蒙</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l19' data-llen='375:398'>　化凌夷而成俗也故咏淑女幾以配上忠孝之篤仁</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l20' data-llen='398:425'>　愛之至也<span class='krp-note'>本/傳</span>楊雄曰關雎作為傷始亂又曰周康之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l21' data-llen='425:448'>　時頌聲作乎下關雎作乎上習治也　李竒曰后夫</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l22' data-llen='448:471'>　人鷄鳴佩玉去君所周康王后不然故詩人歎而傷</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l23' data-llen='471:509'>　之<span class='krp-note'>漢書/注</span>張超曰<span class='krp-note'>康成/弟子</span>關雎畢公作<span class='krp-note'>𥙷傳邕或/云蔡  説</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l24' data-llen='509:532'>　齊詩匡衡曰妃匹之際生民之始萬福之原婚姻之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l25' data-llen='532:558'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '003-2a' );" name="003-2a" class="pb">[003-2a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l26' data-llen='558:581'>　禮也然後品物遂而天命全孔子論詩以關雎為首</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l27' data-llen='581:604'>　言太上者民之父母后夫人之行不侔乎天地則無</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l28' data-llen='604:627'>　以奉神靈之統而理萬物之宜故曰窈窕淑女君子</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l29' data-llen='627:650'>　好逑言能致其貞淑情欲之感無介乎容儀晏私之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l30' data-llen='650:673'>　意不形乎動靜夫然後可以配至尊而為宗廟主此</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l31' data-llen='673:685'>　綱紀之首王敎之端也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l32' data-llen='685:720'>　韓詩關雎刺時也<span class='krp-note'>詩說見内傳及薛君/章句  下關雎夲篇</span>又外傳曰子</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l33' data-llen='720:743'>　夏問關雎何以為風始也子曰關雎至矣乎幽幽㝠</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l34' data-llen='743:769'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '003-2b' );" name="003-2b" class="pb">[003-2b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l35' data-llen='769:792'>　㝠德之所蔵紛紛沸沸道之所行如神龍變化斐斐</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l36' data-llen='792:815'>　文章大哉關雎之道也萬物之所繫羣生之所懸命</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l37' data-llen='815:838'>　也六經之策皆歸論及之盖取之關雎關雎之事大</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l38' data-llen='838:859'>　矣哉天地之間生民之属王道之原不外是矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l39' data-llen='859:882'>　　詩始萌芽申公訓故单行於世故孔安國司馬遷</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l40' data-llen='882:905'>　　劉向揚雄諸人皆宗魯詩至於後漢之末康成未</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l41' data-llen='905:928'>　　見毛傳之先亦逓相祖述韓嬰内傳見于薛君章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l42' data-llen='928:956'>　　句者<span class='krp-note'>詳見/首章</span>與魯畧同唯外傳述夫子之言似與毛</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l43' data-llen='956:982'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '003-3a' );" name="003-3a" class="pb">[003-3a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l44' data-llen='982:1005'>　　合然非其夲論也齊詩匡衡一疏似與魯詩不同</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l45' data-llen='1005:1028'>　　而詩之正義亦未明辨以晢當時儀禮左傳未出</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l46' data-llen='1028:1051'>　　無所考正三家者言未嘗深究夫子不淫不傷之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l47' data-llen='1051:1074'>　　㫖使非毛公出而廓清義将终晦矣竊意康王后</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l48' data-llen='1074:1097'>　　夫人晏起畢公思后妃之徳或弹絃以諷諫事則</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l49' data-llen='1097:1120'>　　有之薛士龍謂關雎刺時是賦其詩者吕元鈞謂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l50' data-llen='1120:1143'>　　陳古以諷是也魯韓傳訛遂直以為刺康后而經</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l51' data-llen='1143:1154'>　　師承之不加察耳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l52' data-llen='1154:1180'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '003-3b' );" name="003-3b" class="pb">[003-3b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l53' data-llen='1180:1203'>　　後漢明帝詔昔應門失守關雎刺世應門失守一</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l54' data-llen='1203:1226'>　　語夲春秋説題辭其言曰人主不正應門失守故</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l55' data-llen='1226:1249'>　　歌關雎以感之然第曰歌以感之不云作以刺時</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l56' data-llen='1249:1272'>　　也後人加以附㑹遂謂康王承文武之盛一朝晏</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l57' data-llen='1272:1295'>　　起夫人不鳴璜宫門不擊柝關雎之人見幾而作</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l58' data-llen='1295:1318'>　　至范蔚宗皇后紀序猶用其説豈止漢魏人哉然</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l59' data-llen='1318:1341'>　　考光武廢郭后詔云既無關雎之徳而有衛霍之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l60' data-llen='1341:1364'>　　風似用毛序即蔚宗序先言后夫人進賢才以輔</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l61' data-llen='1364:1390'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '003-4a' );" name="003-4a" class="pb">[003-4a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l62' data-llen='1390:1421'>　　佐君子衷窈窕而不淫其色<span class='krp-note'>衷誤作哀見/文選李善注</span>是毛説</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l63' data-llen='1421:1444'>　　甚明後又云康王晚朝關雎作諷可知是康王時</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l64' data-llen='1444:1467'>　　人歌關雎以諷諫與薛吕之説正同予故曰康后</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l65' data-llen='1467:1487'>　　晏朝事或有之魯韓雖傳訛非盡無稽也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l66' data-llen='1487:1505'>關關雎鳩在河之洲窈窕淑女君子好逑</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l67' data-llen='1505:1532'>　韓詩内傳曰窈窕貞専淑女奉順坤徳成其紀綱<span class='krp-note'>文/選</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l68' data-llen='1532:1558'>　<span class='krp-note'>注/</span>薛君章句曰詩人言雎鳩貞潔慎匹以聲相求必</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l69' data-llen='1558:1581'>　於河洲蔽隱無人之處故人君動靜退朝入於私宫</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l70' data-llen='1581:1607'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '003-4b' );" name="003-4b" class="pb">[003-4b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l71' data-llen='1607:1630'>　后妃御見去畱有度應門繋柝鼓人上堂退反燕處</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l72' data-llen='1630:1653'>　體安志明今時人君内傾於色賢人見其萌故咏關</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l73' data-llen='1653:1673'>　雎説淑女正容儀以刺時<span class='krp-note'>後漢/書注</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l74' data-llen='1673:1696'>　　按薛君亦云咏以刺時不云作以刺時其文甚明</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l75' data-llen='1696:1719'>　　又漢書注宋均曰應門者人主聽政處也不以政</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l76' data-llen='1719:1742'>　　事為務則有宣淫之心關雎樂而不淫思得賢人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l77' data-llen='1742:1765'>　　與之共化修應門之政云云此又似别為一解矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l78' data-llen='1765:1769'>葛覃</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l79' data-llen='1769:1795'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '003-5a' );" name="003-5a" class="pb">[003-5a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l80' data-llen='1795:1806'>維葉萋萋　是刈是濩</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l81' data-llen='1806:1841'>　韓詩内傳萋萋盛也<span class='krp-note'>文選/注</span>刈取也濩瀹也<span class='krp-note'>釋文字凡/三家  義</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l82' data-llen='1841:1851'>　<span class='krp-note'>異者/俱録</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l83' data-llen='1851:1874'>　　濩毛訓為煮義與韓同爾雅郭注作鑊孫炎曰瀹</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l84' data-llen='1874:1883'>　　謂煮之於鑊</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l85' data-llen='1883:1889'>言告師氏</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l86' data-llen='1889:1919'>　<span class='krp-note'>附/</span>白虎通婦人之所以有師者何學事人之道也<span class='krp-note'>班/氏</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l87' data-llen='1919:1935'>　<span class='krp-note'>説詩雜出三/家不知所傳</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l88' data-llen='1935:1961'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '003-5b' );" name="003-5b" class="pb">[003-5b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l89' data-llen='1961:1965'>卷耳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l90' data-llen='1965:1988'>　晁説之詩序曰魯詩以卷耳鵲巢采蘩采蘋皆康王</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l91' data-llen='1988:2009'>　時詩今無所考意魯詩在北宋時或尚未亡耶</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l92' data-llen='2009:2027'>采采卷耳不盈傾筐嗟我懷人寘彼周行</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l93' data-llen='2027:2050'>　荀子曰傾筐易滿也卷耳易得也然而不可以貳周</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l94' data-llen='2050:2069'>　行故曰心枝則無知傾則不精貳則疑惑</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l95' data-llen='2069:2092'>　　荀為四家所自出故有見即録此説首章義尤精</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l96' data-llen='2092:2115'>　　　左傳以此詩為文王能官人以王及公侯伯子</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l97' data-llen='2115:2141'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '003-6a' );" name="003-6a" class="pb">[003-6a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l98' data-llen='2141:2164'>　　男甸衛采大夫各居其列為周行四家皆同淮南</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l99' data-llen='2164:2187'>　　子引嗟我二句曰以言慕遠世也高誘注思古之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l100' data-llen='2187:2205'>　　賢人各得其行列知漢人無異義矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l101' data-llen='2205:2217'>　韓詩内傳頃筐欹筐也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l102' data-llen='2217:2225'>我姑酌彼金罍</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l103' data-llen='2225:2252'>　韓詩内傳罍天子以玉飾諸侯大夫皆以黄金飾<span class='krp-note'>釋/文</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l104' data-llen='2252:2275'>　又曰金罍大夫器也天子以玉諸侯大夫皆以金士</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l105' data-llen='2275:2298'>　以梓一升曰爵爵盡也足也二升曰觚觚寡也飲當</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l106' data-llen='2298:2324'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '003-6b' );" name="003-6b" class="pb">[003-6b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l107' data-llen='2324:2347'>　寡少三升曰觶觶適也飲當自適四升曰角角觸也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l108' data-llen='2347:2370'>　不能自適觸罪故也五升曰散散訕也飲不自節為</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l109' data-llen='2370:2393'>　人所訕摠名曰爵爵餉也觥亦五升所以罰不敬也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l110' data-llen='2393:2416'>　觥廓也所以著明之貌君子有道廓然著明非所以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l111' data-llen='2416:2434'>　餉不得名觴<span class='krp-note'>儀禮注引/内傳文</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l112' data-llen='2434:2457'>　　知金罍為大夫酒器則非后妃夫人自酌之罍矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l113' data-llen='2457:2463'>云何吁矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l114' data-llen='2463:2478'>　韓詩内傳云辭也<span class='krp-note'>釋/文</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l115' data-llen='2478:2504'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '003-7a' );" name="003-7a" class="pb">[003-7a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l116' data-llen='2504:2508'>樛木</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l117' data-llen='2508:2529'>南有樛木葛藟縈之<span class='krp-note'>樛韓作枓/縈韓作□</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l118' data-llen='2529:2552'>　　按説文枓木高貌韓葢以木之高喻后妃以葛藟</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l119' data-llen='2552:2575'>　　喻衆妾言枓木雖高而葛藟得以□蔓而附焉以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l120' data-llen='2575:2597'>　　興逮下之意與毛詩樛木下曲之訓各有取義</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l121' data-llen='2597:2601'>螽斯</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l122' data-llen='2601:2610'>宜爾子孫繩繩兮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l123' data-llen='2610:2625'>　韓詩外傳言母賢能使子賢也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l124' data-llen='2625:2651'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '003-7b' );" name="003-7b" class="pb">[003-7b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l125' data-llen='2651:2674'>　　繩繩毛訓戒慎也正是子賢之意興振振蟄蟄皆</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l126' data-llen='2674:2683'>　　當依古為訓</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l127' data-llen='2683:2688'>兔置</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l128' data-llen='2688:2701'>施于中逵<span class='krp-note'>逵韓/作馗</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l129' data-llen='2701:2716'>　韓詩薛君章句馗中九交之道</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l130' data-llen='2716:2739'>　　爾雅一逹謂之道路二逹謂之岐旁三逹謂之劇</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l131' data-llen='2739:2762'>　　旁四逹謂之衢五逹謂之康六逹謂之莊七逹謂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l132' data-llen='2762:2785'>　　之劇驂八逹謂之崇期九逹謂之馗郭注四道交</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l133' data-llen='2785:2811'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '003-8a' );" name="003-8a" class="pb">[003-8a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l134' data-llen='2811:2821'>　　出復有旁通者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l135' data-llen='2821:2825'>芣苢</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l136' data-llen='2825:2848'>　魯詩劉向列女傳蔡人之妻宋人之女也夫有惡疾</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l137' data-llen='2848:2871'>　其母將改嫁之女曰夫之不幸女之不幸也且夫采</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l138' data-llen='2871:2894'>　采芣苢之草雖其臭惡猶始于采埓之终于懷襭之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l139' data-llen='2894:2912'>　況于夫婦之道乎其母乃作芣苢之詩</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l140' data-llen='2912:2931'>　韓序芣苢傷夫有惡疾也<span class='krp-note'>文選/注</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l141' data-llen='2931:2954'>　　按劉峻辨命論冉耕歌其芣苢即伯牛也論語伯</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l142' data-llen='2954:2980'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '003-8b' );" name="003-8b" class="pb">[003-8b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l143' data-llen='2980:3003'>　　牛有疾注曰癩疾是也然宋母恐只是歌芣苢而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l144' data-llen='3003:3018'>　　非作也亦疑傳訛當如毛傳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l145' data-llen='3018:3028'>采采芣苢薄言采之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l146' data-llen='3028:3051'>　韓詩内傳曰直曰車前瞿曰芣苢　薛君曰芣苢澤</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l147' data-llen='3051:3074'>　㵼也臭惡之草詩人傷其君子有惡疾人道不通求</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l148' data-llen='3074:3097'>　已不得發憤而作以是興芣苢雖臭惡乎我猶采取</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l149' data-llen='3097:3120'>　而不已者以興君子雖有惡疾我猶守而不離去也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l150' data-llen='3120:3143'>　　夫有惡疾妻不肯去列女傳猶為近理若求已不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l151' data-llen='3143:3169'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '003-9a' );" name="003-9a" class="pb">[003-9a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l152' data-llen='3169:3192'>　　得發憤而作則夫子何取而入之三百篇乎　毛</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l153' data-llen='3192:3215'>　　以車前為芣苢韓曰直為車前瞿為芣苢則似二</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l154' data-llen='3215:3238'>　　物薛漢又指澤㵼是非臭惡之草也按陸佃釋韓</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l155' data-llen='3238:3261'>　　傳云車前一名牛舌與澤㵼同又云生于両旁謂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l156' data-llen='3261:3271'>　　之瞿可以治癩</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l157' data-llen='3271:3275'>漢廣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l158' data-llen='3275:3302'>　韓序漢廣悅人也<span class='krp-note'>文選/注</span>薛君章句曰游女漢神也言</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l159' data-llen='3302:3315'>　漢神時見不可求而得之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l160' data-llen='3315:3341'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '003-9b' );" name="003-9b" class="pb">[003-9b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l161' data-llen='3341:3364'>　　韓云悅人葢悅游女之貞潔而思欲求之耳薛君</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l162' data-llen='3364:3387'>　　乃以游女為漢神類陳思感甄后而賦洛神悖矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l163' data-llen='3387:3410'>　　　不可休息韓作不可求思孔穎逹曰詩之大體</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l164' data-llen='3410:3433'>　　韻在辭上休求二字為韻二息字俱當依韓作思</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l165' data-llen='3433:3437'>汝墳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l166' data-llen='3437:3460'>　魯詩劉向曰周南大夫平治水土過時不來其妻恐</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l167' data-llen='3460:3483'>　其觧于王事葢與其鄰人陳素所與大夫言國家多</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l168' data-llen='3483:3506'>　難唯勉强之無有譴怒遺父母憂生于亂世迫于暴</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l169' data-llen='3506:3533'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '003-10a' );" name="003-10a" class="pb">[003-10a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l170' data-llen='3533:3557'>　虐然而仕者為父母在也乃作詩云云<span class='krp-note'>列女/傳</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l171' data-llen='3557:3580'>　韓詩汝濆辭家也王室政敎如烈火矣猶觸冒而仕</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l172' data-llen='3580:3604'>　者以父母甚迫近饑寒之憂為此禄仕<span class='krp-note'>漢書/注</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l173' data-llen='3604:3627'>　　毛序婦人閔其君子能勉之以正也正與魯合所</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l174' data-llen='3627:3650'>　　謂無遺父母憂者王政酷烈恐罪及其親也韓以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l175' data-llen='3650:3673'>　　家貧禄仕為義亦不貼文王身上說如集傳所云</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l176' data-llen='3673:3696'>　　也後漢周磐嘗讀是詩而起思親之慕若曰王政</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l177' data-llen='3696:3719'>　　雖迫如火矣其如我父母何其情愴然感人千載</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l178' data-llen='3719:3746'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '003-10b' );" name="003-10b" class="pb">[003-10b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l179' data-llen='3746:3754'>　　古義長矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l180' data-llen='3754:3800'>遵彼汝墳<span class='krp-note'>韓作/濆</span>惄如調饑<span class='krp-note'>惄韓作愵/調作朝</span>王室如燬<span class='krp-note'>韓作<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR1754' title='KR1754' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR1754.png'/>/火尾反</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l181' data-llen='3800:3824'><span class='krp-note'>齊人曰燬/楚人曰<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR1754' title='KR1754' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR1754.png'/></span>父母孔邇</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l182' data-llen='3824:3851'>　韓詩薛君曰朝饑最難忍<span class='krp-note'>文選/注</span>　按韓詩濆水名也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l183' data-llen='3851:3874'>　　楊慎曰調饑或作輖饑皆屬魯魚焦氏易林㑂如</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l184' data-llen='3874:3892'>　　旦饑郭遐周詩惄焉如朝饑皆作朝</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l185' data-llen='3892:3922'>　韓詩内傳赬赤也<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR1754' title='KR1754' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR1754.png'/>烈火孔甚也邇近也言魴魚勞</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l186' data-llen='3922:3941'>　則尾赤君子勞則顔色變<span class='krp-note'>漢書/注</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l187' data-llen='3941:3968'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '003-11a' );" name="003-11a" class="pb">[003-11a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l188' data-llen='3968:4013'>草蟲<span class='krp-note'>曹粹中詩説曰齊詩先采蘋而后草蟲王應麟亦/云未知何本按儀禮歌召南三篇原以草蟲在先</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l189' data-llen='4013:4036'>　魯詩劉向曰孔子曰未見君子憂心惙惙亦旣見止</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l190' data-llen='4036:4062'>　亦旣覯止我心則悦詩之好善道之甚也如此<span class='krp-note'>説/苑</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l191' data-llen='4062:4084'>　　按劉以思君子為好善道則非大夫妻所作矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l192' data-llen='4084:4088'>采蘋</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l193' data-llen='4088:4111'>　　禮記采蘩樂不失職也采蘋樂循法也初不言大</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l194' data-llen='4111:4134'>　　夫妻能承祭祀左傳始以采蘋采蘩為昭忠信澗</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l195' data-llen='4134:4157'>　　溪沼沚之毛蘋蘩薀藻之菜可薦於鬼神羞於王</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l196' data-llen='4157:4184'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '003-11b' );" name="003-11b" class="pb">[003-11b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l197' data-llen='4184:4207'>　　公又曰濟澤之阿行潦之蘋藻寘之宗室季蘭尸</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l198' data-llen='4207:4230'>　　之敬也似以二篇通美大夫妻之作亦未明季蘭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l199' data-llen='4230:4253'>　　為何時人要之毛説為有據矣三家他無所考惟</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l200' data-llen='4253:4276'>　　晁説之所見魯詩以鵲巢采蘩采蘋皆康王時詩</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l201' data-llen='4276:4288'>　　則與毛公時世不合</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l202' data-llen='4288:4295'>采蘋　采藻</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l203' data-llen='4295:4313'>　韓詩沈者曰蘋浮者曰藻<span class='krp-note'>釋/文</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l204' data-llen='4313:4336'>　　郭璞曰蘋水上浮萍也江東人謂之薸陸佃曰藻</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l205' data-llen='4336:4363'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '003-12a' );" name="003-12a" class="pb">[003-12a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l206' data-llen='4363:4386'>　　生水底有二種　萍藻即祭統所云水草之葅又</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l207' data-llen='4386:4409'>　　昏禮云芼之以蘋藻則兼可生用矣關雎之采荇</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l208' data-llen='4409:4422'>　　所以備祭品叅觀甚明</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l209' data-llen='4422:4426'>甘棠</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l210' data-llen='4426:4450'>　魯詩史記召伯廵行鄉邑有棠𣗳決政事其下人思</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l211' data-llen='4450:4474'>　召公懷棠𣗳不敢伐故歌咏之　劉向曰召公述職</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l212' data-llen='4474:4497'>　當蠺桑之時不欲變民事故不入邑中舎於甘棠之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l213' data-llen='4497:4512'>　下而聴斷焉後世思而歌咏之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l214' data-llen='4512:4539'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '003-12b' );" name="003-12b" class="pb">[003-12b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l215' data-llen='4539:4562'>　韓詩外傳召伯在朝有司請營洛以居召伯曰嗟以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l216' data-llen='4562:4585'>　吾一身而勞百姓非吾先君文王之志也於是出而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l217' data-llen='4585:4608'>　就蒸庶於隴畆阡陌之間而聴斷焉召伯暴處百姓</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l218' data-llen='4608:4631'>　大悦耕桑者倍力以勸於是歳大稔民給家足其後</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l219' data-llen='4631:4654'>　在位者驕奢不恤元元耕桑失時於是詩人見召伯</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l220' data-llen='4654:4668'>　之所休息𣗳下美而歌之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l221' data-llen='4668:4691'>　　孔叢子曰吾于甘棠見宗廟之所以敬也尊其人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l222' data-llen='4691:4715'>　　必敬其位左傳引此詩亦曰思其人猶愛其𣗳皆</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l223' data-llen='4715:4742'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '003-13a' );" name="003-13a" class="pb">[003-13a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l224' data-llen='4742:4765'>　　以召伯旣沒而民歌其徳也魯韓詞異而大㫖同</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l225' data-llen='4765:4769'>行露</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l226' data-llen='4769:4792'>　魯詩劉向曰召南申女者申人之女也旣許嫁于酆</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l227' data-llen='4792:4815'>　夫家禮不備而往迎之女與其人言夫婦者人倫之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l228' data-llen='4815:4838'>　始不可不正夫家輕禮違制不可以行夫家訟之于</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l229' data-llen='4838:4861'>　理女終以一禮不備持義不往而作詩曰雖速我獄</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l230' data-llen='4861:4884'>　室家不足君子以為得婦道之宜故舉而揚之傳而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l231' data-llen='4884:4901'>　法之以絶無禮之求防淫慾之行焉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l232' data-llen='4901:4928'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '003-13b' );" name="003-13b" class="pb">[003-13b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l233' data-llen='4928:4951'>　韓詩外傳曰行露之人許嫁矣然而未往也見一物</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l234' data-llen='4951:4974'>　不具一禮未備守志貞禮守死不往君子以為得婦</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l235' data-llen='4974:4997'>　道之宜故舉而傳之楊而歌之以絶無禮之求防汙</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l236' data-llen='4997:5003'>　道之行</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l237' data-llen='5003:5026'>　　毛傳不言申女之事但云衰亂之俗微貞信之敎</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l238' data-llen='5026:5049'>　　興强暴之男不能侵凌貞女夫强暴尚凌貞女則</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l239' data-llen='5049:5072'>　　未為化行而俗美矣但如魯韓説以閨門之處子</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l240' data-llen='5072:5095'>　　求全責備至于搆訟不顧豈無父母之命媒妁之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l241' data-llen='5095:5122'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '003-14a' );" name="003-14a" class="pb">[003-14a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l242' data-llen='5122:5145'>　　言乎意者夫家必可以備禮而不備以致夫家搆</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l243' data-llen='5145:5165'>　　訟其女在家守禮自矢詩人舉而揚之耳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l244' data-llen='5165:5169'>羔羊</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l245' data-llen='5169:5187'>羔羊之皮素絲五紽退食自公委蛇委蛇</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l246' data-llen='5187:5210'>　韓詩内傳小曰羔大曰羊素喻潔白絲喻柔屈紽數</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l247' data-llen='5210:5242'>　名也逶迤<span class='krp-note'>本作/逶迤</span>公正貌<span class='krp-note'>正/義</span>　薛君曰詩人賢仕為大</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l248' data-llen='5242:5265'>　夫者其徳能稱有潔白之性柔屈之行進退有度數</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l249' data-llen='5265:5275'>　也<span class='krp-note'>漢書/注</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l250' data-llen='5275:5302'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '003-14b' );" name="003-14b" class="pb">[003-14b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l251' data-llen='5302:5325'>　　以逶迤為公正與毛傳行可從迹之意不同而韓</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l252' data-llen='5325:5332'>　　説較明</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l253' data-llen='5332:5337'>摽有梅</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l254' data-llen='5337:5354'>摽有梅其實七兮求我庶士迨其吉兮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l255' data-llen='5354:5376'>　韓詩摽作莩傳曰莩零落也迨願也<span class='krp-note'>釋/文</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l256' data-llen='5376:5399'>　　王應麟曰摽與莩通非是莩是零落之意摽乃擊</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l257' data-llen='5399:5422'>　　之使落與寤辟有摽之訓為拊心同願者父母之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l258' data-llen='5422:5443'>　　願戴岷隱鼠璞曰此擇婿之詞父母之心也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l259' data-llen='5443:5470'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '003-15a' );" name="003-15a" class="pb">[003-15a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l260' data-llen='5470:5474'>小星</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l261' data-llen='5474:5480'>寔命不同</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l262' data-llen='5480:5498'>　韓詩寔作實傳曰實有也<span class='krp-note'>釋/文</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l263' data-llen='5498:5521'>　　寔與實不通大雅實墉實壑注實當作寔按寔音</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l264' data-llen='5521:5544'>　　同室寔是也實有也韓若曰宵征之所以肅肅者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l265' data-llen='5544:5557'>　　有命自天不得而同也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l266' data-llen='5557:5562'>江有汜</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l267' data-llen='5562:5567'>江有渚</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l268' data-llen='5567:5594'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '003-15b' );" name="003-15b" class="pb">[003-15b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l269' data-llen='5594:5612'>　韓詩内傳一溢一否曰渚<span class='krp-note'>釋/文</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l270' data-llen='5612:5618'>何彼穠矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l271' data-llen='5618:5641'>　魯詩鄭箴膏肓曰齊侯嫁女以其母王姬治嫁之車</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l272' data-llen='5641:5669'>　遠送之<span class='krp-note'>儀禮/疏</span>　<span class='krp-note'>此為魯詩説見/康成答張逸語</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l273' data-llen='5669:5692'>　　毛傳謂武王女文王孫適齊侯之子以平王為平</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l274' data-llen='5692:5715'>　　正之王葢以二南為文王時詩故其説如此集傳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l275' data-llen='5715:5738'>　　亦無定見夫太公之女為武王元妃似不應以女</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l276' data-llen='5738:5766'>　　復嫁齊侯之子<span class='krp-note'>毛竒/齡説</span>且武王五男二女元女嫁陳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l277' data-llen='5766:5793'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '003-16a' );" name="003-16a" class="pb">[003-16a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l278' data-llen='5793:5816'>　　不聞次女嫁吕伋也集傳載或説謂平王宜臼之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l279' data-llen='5816:5839'>　　孫嫁齊釐侯之子以齊桓娶共姬事見春秋也似</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l280' data-llen='5839:5862'>　　為可據然共姬為莊王女乃平王之曾孫矣諸説</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l281' data-llen='5862:5885'>　　紛如莫知誰是不如魯詩以齊侯之子為齊侯之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l282' data-llen='5885:5908'>　　女子以平王之孫為王之外孫女似可解紛　穠</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l283' data-llen='5908:5927'>　　韓詩作茙説文云衣厚貌亦與毛傳異</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l284' data-llen='5927:5931'>騶虞</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l285' data-llen='5931:5958'>　魯詩古有梁騶者天子之田也<span class='krp-note'>文選/注</span>賈誼曰騶者文</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l286' data-llen='5958:5985'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '003-16b' );" name="003-16b" class="pb">[003-16b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l287' data-llen='5985:6008'>　王之囿虞者囿之司獸者虞人翼五豝以待一發所</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l288' data-llen='6008:6023'>　以復中也<span class='krp-note'>太𫝊/新書</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l289' data-llen='6023:6046'>　　周禮樂以騶虞疏曰騶虞天子掌鳥獸之官也禮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l290' data-llen='6046:6069'>　　記射義曰騶虞者樂官備也古以騶虞為官名魯</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l291' data-llen='6069:6092'>　　詩正與之合毛傳不如魯長故歐陽公主之　墨</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l292' data-llen='6092:6115'>　　子曰成王因先王之樂命曰騶虞晁説之言魯詩</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l293' data-llen='6115:6138'>　　謂詩作於康王之世皆無他書可證文選注引琴</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l294' data-llen='6138:6157'>　　操曰鄒虞邵國之女所作也未知何本</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l295' data-llen='6157:6184'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '003-17a' );" name="003-17a" class="pb">[003-17a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l296' data-llen='6184:6195'>壹發五豝吁嗟乎騶虞</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l297' data-llen='6195:6218'>　魯詩鄭氏曰壹發五豝喻得賢者多也吁嗟乎騶虞</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l298' data-llen='6218:6246'>　嘆仁也<span class='krp-note'>射義注詩鄭注三禮時/未見毛  所説皆魯詩</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l299' data-llen='6246:6260'>　韓詩吁嗟嘆詞<span class='krp-note'>釋/文</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l300' data-llen='6260:6283'>　　鄭以騶虞為嘆仁人者以騶虞之官亦仁人也周</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l301' data-llen='6283:6306'>　　書王㑹篇曰壹發五豝言多賢也盖五豝五豵皆</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l302' data-llen='6306:6329'>　　以多為喻騶虞之官莫非仁賢則其得人之多而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l303' data-llen='6329:6352'>　　官之備可見故詩人嗟嘆而美之　戴埴鼠璞曰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l304' data-llen='6352:6379'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0062', 'WYG', '003-17b' );" name="003-17b" class="pb">[003-17b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l305' data-llen='6379:6396'>　　騶者如七騶六騶虞如山虞澤虞</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l306' data-llen='6396:6399'>　</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l307' data-llen='6399:6402'>　</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l308' data-llen='6402:6405'>　</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l309' data-llen='6405:6408'>　</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l310' data-llen='6408:6411'>　</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l311' data-llen='6411:6414'>　</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l312' data-llen='6414:6424'>　三家詩拾遺卷三</span><br/>
